## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **revumenib Revuforj 2024** = first FDA menin inhibitor — KMT2A-rearranged + NPM1-mutated AML. menin-KMT2A interface 가 FDA 첫 승인된 protein-protein interaction 표적 in AML. quantum-VQE 의 PPI scaffold 가 직접 fit. ziftomenib (research) 가 second-gen 후속 (cross-bone_marrow_failure Q-4).
2. **venetoclax + azacitidine VIALE-A 2020** = first new 1L AML chemo-ineligible elderly in 40+ years. 50+ year 7+3 cytotoxic-only era 종료. BCL-2 + HMA combo paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 BCL-2 pocket fit + HMA mechanism orthogonal.
3. **FLT3 inhibitor 3 (midostaurin 2017 + gilteritinib 2018 + quizartinib 2023)** = AML first targeted era + 1L paradigm shift. midostaurin = first FLT3 + chemo combo. gilteritinib = R/R single agent. quizartinib = 1L FLT3-ITD frontline 2023 paradigm shift. quantum-VQE FLT3-ITD vs TKD selectivity 직접 fit.
4. **IDH inhibitor 3 (ivosidenib 2018 + enasidenib 2017 + olutasidenib 2022)** = AML 만성 + IDH1/2m 표적 era. ivosidenib 1L AML 2019 + MDS 2024 expansion. enasidenib R/R AML. olutasidenib R/R AML IDH1. quantum-VQE 의 IDH R132H + R140Q + R172K allele selectivity fit.
5. **gemtuzumab ozogamicin Mylotarg 2000/2017** = first CD33 ADC — AML calicheamicin payload. 2000 first approval → 2010 voluntary withdrawal (toxicity) → 2017 re-approval (lower dose fractionated). quantum-VQE 의 CD33 epitope + linker + payload-release fit.
6. **daunorubicin + cytarabine liposomal Vyxeos 2017** = first FDA pediatric AML + secondary AML 5:1 ratio liposomal. dual encapsulation pharmacokinetics. 50+ year 7+3 anthracycline + cytarabine backbone 의 modern reformulation.
7. **glasdegib Daurismo 2018** = first FDA Hh (Smoothened) inhibitor in AML + low-dose cytarabine combo. Hedgehog pathway = LSC quiescence regulator. quantum-VQE 의 Smoothened pocket leverage.
8. **magrolimab anti-CD47 Phase 3 fail 2023** = paradigm cautionary tale. CD47 "do not eat me" macrophage checkpoint. 2023 ENHANCE-3 + ENHANCE-2 Phase 3 fail (MDS + AML). quantum-VQE in-silico 가 wet-lab/clinical translation gap 직시 (cross-mds_specific).
9. **allogeneic HSCT (matched sibling + matched unrelated + haplo)** = 만성 AML 1차 cure modality (especially adverse-risk + R/R). venetoclax+aza/FLT3i/IDHi 가 bridging therapy. GvHD + GvL 만성 long-term issue (cross-bone_marrow_failure + transplant + hsct_gvhd_specific).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, AML 임상 의미 한정. 한국 K-AML 식약처 framework + 산정특례 administrative lens 한정.

